# Templates for Scrum-board

## Template for Tasks:
  #36 Title (same as on its user story's "Confirmation"-list)

  [Assigned: Name]
  [Size: Size]

## Template for User Stories:
  #7.2 Title (same as on its epic's "Confirmation"-list)
  <details open>
  <summary>User Story</summary>
  <br>
  As a user, I want to ..., so that ....
  </details>

  ## Confirmation
  - [ ] (task here)

## Template for Epics:
  Title
  ## Confirmation
  - [ ] (user story here)
